Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:53.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tin ton tan 跨出那一步的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:58.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}世界就像全景畫一樣 展開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:04.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 無論天空有多寬闊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:10.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}如果只有我一人 肯定不會在意
